  }, "Getting the Right Tools"), mdx("p", null, "I had the idea in 2019, but didn\u2019t really know how to make it into reality. I\u2019m an experienced React developer, but otherwise I didn\u2019t have the proper knowledge of what technologies to use."), mdx("p", null, "In March 2020, I found out that Letterboxd uses a free API called ", mdx("a", {
